                  "blocks": {}
                },
                "tab_content_XQxQJV": {
                  "type": "tab_content",
                  "name": "Tab content",
                  "settings": {
                    "label": "Product",
                    "hash_target": "",
                    "tab_group": "0",
                    "custom_css": "& {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 24px;\n}",
                    "generate_block_presets": "never",
                    "category_name": "",
                    "hidden_name_backup": ""
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "collapsible_HJ6jbB": {
                      "type": "collapsible",
                      "name": "Collapsible",
                      "settings": {
                        "label": "<strong>What makes your weight management supplements different?</strong>",
                        "metafield_namespace_key": "product.smart.faqs",
                        "metafield_image_key": "image",
                        "metafield_label_key": "question",
                        "accordion_class": "accordion",
                        "content": "<p>Most weight management supplements rely on stimulants, diuretics, or proprietary blends that promise a lot and deliver water weight. We took a different approach. Every formula in this collection is built around clinically studied ingredients at clinically studied doses, delivered through Capsoil® absorption technology — so what you take actually reaches your system. No caffeine. No fillers. No guesswork. Just real metabolic support backed by human research.</p>",
                        "show": false,
                        "metafield_content_key": "answer",
                        "metafield_default_state": "open_first",
                        "auto_close_siblings": true,
                        "dynamic_content_type": "default",
                        "custom_css": "& {\n}",
                        "hide_if_empty": "none"
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    },
                    "collapsible_AgjWig": {
                      "type": "collapsible",
                      "name": "Collapsible",
                      "settings": {
                        "label": "<strong>Can I take these alongside my current routine?</strong>",
                        "metafield_namespace_key": "product.smart.faqs",
                        "metafield_image_key": "image",
                        "metafield_label_key": "question",
                        "accordion_class": "accordion",
                        "content": "<p>Yes, these formulas are designed to complement a healthy lifestyle, not replace it. They work best when paired with balanced nutrition, regular movement, and consistent sleep. If you take prescription medication or have an underlying health condition, check with your healthcare provider before adding any new supplement to your routine.</p>",
                        "show": false,
                        "metafield_content_key": "answer",
                        "metafield_default_state": "open_first",
                        "auto_close_siblings": true,
                        "dynamic_content_type": "default",
                        "custom_css": "& {\n}",
                        "hide_if_empty": "none"
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    },
                    "collapsible_awmprm": {
                      "type": "collapsible",
                      "name": "Collapsible",
                      "settings": {
                        "label": "What's The Absorption Company's approach to weight management?",
                        "metafield_namespace_key": "product.smart.faqs",
                        "metafield_image_key": "image",
                        "metafield_label_key": "question",
                        "accordion_class": "accordion",
                        "content": "<p>We believe most supplements fail for one reason: your body never absorbs enough of the active ingredients to make a difference. So we focused on solving that first. Every formula starts with clinically studied ingredients at the doses used in research, then we apply Capsoil® absorption technology to deliver them at up to 20× higher bioavailability. The result is a smaller, smarter, stimulant-free approach to weight management — built on science, not shortcuts.</p>",
                        "show": false,
                        "metafield_content_key": "answer",
                        "metafield_default_state": "open_first",
                        "auto_close_siblings": true,
                        "dynamic_content_type": "default",
                        "custom_css": "& {\n}",
                        "hide_if_empty": "none"
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    },
                    "collapsible_4LdAAF": {
                      "type": "collapsible",
                      "name": "Collapsible",
                      "settings": {
                        "label": "<strong>How long until I see results?</strong>",
                        "metafield_namespace_key": "product.smart.faqs",
                        "metafield_image_key": "image",
                        "metafield_label_key": "question",
                        "accordion_class": "accordion",
                        "content": "<p>Sustainable weight management isn't overnight, and any product promising otherwise is selling you something else. Most people start noticing shifts in appetite and cravings within the first few weeks, with more meaningful changes in body composition over 2 to 4 months of consistent use. The clinical studies behind our key ingredients ran anywhere from 4 weeks to 16 weeks, with results building over time. Pair that with consistent habits and you're set up for the long game, not the quick fix.</p>",
                        "show": false,
                        "metafield_content_key": "answer",
                        "metafield_default_state": "open_first",
                        "auto_close_siblings": true,
                        "dynamic_content_type": "default",
                        "custom_css": "& {\n}",
                        "hide_if_empty": "none"
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    },
                    "collapsible_PUaxVh": {
                      "type": "collapsible",
                      "name": "Collapsible",
                      "settings": {
                        "label": "<strong>Why is absorption such a big deal for weight management?</strong>",
                        "metafield_namespace_key": "product.smart.faqs",
                        "metafield_image_key": "image",
                        "metafield_label_key": "question",
                        "accordion_class": "accordion",
                        "content": "<p>Because the ingredient on the label only matters if your body can actually use it. Most weight management supplements lose a significant percentage of their active compounds before they ever reach your bloodstream — meaning you're paying for ingredients that never do their job. That's why we built every formula in this collection on Capsoil® absorption technology, which has been shown in human testing to deliver up to 20× better bioavailability. Better absorption means the clinically studied doses on the label are the doses your body actually receives.</p>",
                        "show": false,
                        "metafield_content_key": "answer",
